criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients undergoing endoscopic ultrasound for evaluation of pancreatic cysts
             (including pseudocysts and suspected pancreatic cystic neoplasms) in the
             gastrointestinal (GI) lab at Mayo Clinic Jacksonville.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Unwilling/unable to consent;

          -  Solid pancreatic mass on computerized axial tomography/magnetic resonance (CT/MR);

          -  Allergy to Fluorescein;

          -  Pregnancy.
